tune.name: Nicola Braid's Strathspey
tune.author: Mikael Georgii
tune.content:
\relative f' <<
  {
    \clef treble
    \key a \major
    \time 4/4

    \repeat volta 2 {
      \partial 4 e4 |
      a8. cis16 b8. a16 b8. a16 fis16 a8. |
      e8. fis16 e cis8. e4 fis8. gis16 |
      a8. b16 cis a8. fis'8. e16 d cis8. |
      b8. cis16 b fis8. b4 e, |
      \break

      a8. cis16 b8. a16 b8. a16 fis a8. |
      e8. fis16 e cis8. e4 fis8. gis16 |
      a8. b16 cis a8. fis' e16 d cis8. |
      b8. a16 b cis8. a4
    } \break

    \repeat volta 2 {
      b4 |
      cis8. b16 a cis8. b a16 gis f8. |
      fis8. gis16 a8. b16 cis4. cis8 |
      d8. cis16 b d8. cis8. b16 a cis8. |
      b8. a16 gis fis8. f4 cis |
      \break

      a'8. gis16 fis a8. gis fis16 f gis8. |
      fis8. gis16 a8. b16 cis4. cis8 |
      d8. cis16 b d8. cis8. b16 a cis8. |
      b8. a16 b cis8. a4
    }
   }

  \new ChordNames {
    \chordmode {
      s4 |
      a2 d | e a | fis:m d | b/dis e |
      a2 d | e a | a/cis d4 fis:m/b | e2:7 a4

      s4 |
      fis2:m cis:7 | fis:m fis:m/cis | b:m fis:m/a | c:dim cis |
      fis2:m cis:7/gis | fis:m/a fis:7 | b4:m e a fis:m | b:m/d e a
    }
  }
>>
